name: Chess
description:
Chess is a two-player board game of strategy and intellect. Players maneuver their pieces across a checkered board to capture the opponents
 king. It requires tactical thinking, planning, and foresight. The game is played with 16 pieces per player and involves unique movements 
 for each piece. Chess is renowned for its complexity and is enjoyed by people of all ages.

name: Bubble shooter extreme
description: Bubble Shooter Extreme is a WebGL/HTML5 version of popular Bubble Shooter game with great graphics. Shoot two or more connected bubbles of the same color to disappear them. The more bubbles you disappear in one shot the more score you get. Game is won after all bubbles exploded.

name: Checkers
description:
Checkers is played by two persons who oppose each other across a board
            of 64 light and dark squares, the same as a chessboard. The 24 playing
            pieces are disk-shaped and of contrasting colours (whatever their
            colours, they are identified as black and white).

name: Reversi
description:
Each piece played must be laid adjacent to an opponent's piece so that
            the opponent's piece or a row of opponent's pieces is flanked by the
            new piece and another piece of the player's colour

name: Car Driving Simulator
description: Play this Extreme Car Driving Simulator game to display power drift car with drag racing in new games to become real drift master. Drive as fast as you can and explore extreme roads and ramps to let your car perform amazing stunts. This is a 3D driving game with amazing drifting cars that shows your driving skills to control power drift cars in Extreme Car Driving Simulator

name: Real Shooting Fps Strike
description: Real Shooting Fps Strike is a well-made 3D gun battle survival game. Shoot the enemies pouring in from all directions and defeat them. Can you complete all levels and get all the weapons? Choose the gun you like and start fighting! I wish you success and have fun!

name: Goodgame Empire
description: Goodgame Empire is a great strategy MMO by Good-game Studios. Build your own castle, create a powerful army and fight epic player versus player battles on a dynamic world map. Crush your enemies, conquer land and rise to be the ruler of a mighty empire!
